How to run these program
------------------------
-> enter make command to compile the program
-> enter make run command to run the both program
(you can change the nofThread variable to pass the cmd argument for nthreads.c )

References
----------
->https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/mutex-lock-for-linux-thread-synchronization/
->https://www.cs.cmu.edu/afs/cs/academic/class/15492-f07/www/pthreads.html
